strings.DV_WEB_DP_popover_purchase_rights:
{paragraph}When you buy a video, your viewing rights don’t expire, except as detailed in the {link|touLink}Terms of Use{end}. You can Watch
                        Now or Download the video to a {link|compatibleDeviceLink}compatible device{end}, except for Pay-Per-View videos.
                        Pay-Per-View videos will become available to watch once the event starts, will be available for replay for 24 hours
                        following the event, and are not available for download.{end}
                        {paragraph}If you choose Watch Now, the video will instantly stream to your computer and you may later stream it on another
                        compatible device. If downloading is available, you can {link|learnDownloading}download the video{end} to two locations. This
                        enables you to watch the video without an Internet connection.{end}
                        {paragraph}Some new release movies become unavailable for downloading for a limited time due to licensing restrictions. If
                        applicable, we will notify you about this before processing your order.{end}
                        {paragraph}Additional restrictions may apply. For more information, go to the {link|touLink}Terms of Use{end}.{end}
